name: Jonathan Sahagun
text: The other day pumunta ako sa Jollibee. Grabe ang bilis ng service! Tapos mas juicylicious ang Chickenjoy, at mas malamig na yung iced tea! Ang laki talagang pagkakaiba from just a year ago. Even the people around me noticed! Wow, REAL CHANGE has come talaga. Good job, PRRD!  👊
